Package: wormsplot
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Visualizing the Movements of Historical Figures
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-04-09
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: dplyr, tidyr, ggplot2
Author: Louis Teitelbaum <louist@post.bgu.ac.il>
Maintainer: Louis Teitelbaum <louist@post.bgu.ac.il>
Description: The `wormsplot` package can be used to easily visualize the lives of
    historical figures as they moved from place to place. Expanding on `ggplot2`,
    the package provides a new geom, `geom_worm`, which allows for an arbitrary
    number of moves within each worm, and takes intuitively structured data input.
    The package also includes a convenience function, `wormsplot`, for generating
    aesthetic plots with minimal effort.
License: GPL-2
